    <!-- Tower Info Descriptions -->
    <string name="tower_upgrades_info"><b>Upgrade System</b>\n\n<b>Max Level:</b> 5\n\n<b>Upgrade Cost:</b> Base Cost × 2^Level\n• Level 1→2: Base Cost × 2\n• Level 2→3: Base Cost × 4\n• Level 3→4: Base Cost × 8\n• Level 4→5: Base Cost × 16\n\n<b>Stat Improvements per Level:</b>\n• Damage: +20%\n• Range: +10%\n• Fire Rate: +20%\n\n<b>Strategy Tip:</b> Upgrade your best-positioned towers first to maximize their effectiveness throughout the game!</string>
    <string name="firewall_tower_info"><b>Firewall Tower</b>\n\nCost: 200\nDamage: 10\nRange: 150\nFire Rate: 2.0/sec\n\n<b>Ability:</b> Applies a burn effect that deals damage over time (50% of direct damage for 2.5 seconds). Gains penetration chance with upgrades, potentially damaging multiple enemies.</string>
    <string name="honeypot_tower_info" tools:ignore="StringFormatInvalid"><b>Honeypot Tower</b>\n\nCost: 300\nDamage: 15\nRange: 120\nFire Rate: 1.5/sec\n\n<b>Ability:</b> Covers enemies in sticky glue, slowing their movement by 50% for 3 seconds. Excellent for controlling enemy movement and creating choke points.</string>
    <string name="jammer_tower_info"><b>Jammer Tower</b>\n\nCost: 400\nDamage: 10\nRange: 200\nFire Rate: 3.0/sec\n\n<b>Ability:</b> Stuns enemies for 0.5 seconds with very fast attack speed. Wide range makes it ideal for covering large areas and hitting multiple targets.</string>

    <!-- Enemy Info Descriptions -->
    <string name="data_crawler_info"><b>Data Crawler</b>\n\nHealth: 50\nSpeed: 120\nReward: 5 resources\nDamage: 5\n\n<b>Description:</b> Fast-moving web scraping bots with low health. They move quickly but are easy to destroy. Good for farming early resources.</string>
    <string name="virus_bot_info"><b>Virus Bot</b>\n\nHealth: 100\nSpeed: 100\nReward: 10 resources\nDamage: 10\n\n<b>Description:</b> Virus-infected systems with moderate health and speed. Appears starting from wave 5. A balanced threat that requires attention.</string>
    <string name="trojan_horse_info"><b>Trojan Horse</b>\n\nHealth: 200\nSpeed: 80\nReward: 20 resources\nDamage: 20\n\n<b>Description:</b> Sophisticated malware systems that are slow but extremely tanky. Appears starting from wave 10. Requires concentrated fire from multiple towers.</string>
